{"surah":{"number":50,"name":"ق","englishName":"Qaf","englishTranslation":"The Letter \"Qaf\"","ayahCount":45},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:13.766Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"Qaf. By the honored Qur'an...","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قٓ ۚ","english":"Qaf","translit":"qaf","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱلْقُرْءَانِ","english":"By the Quran","translit":"wal-qur'āni","root":"قرأ","audio":"wbw/050_001_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَجِيدِ","english":"the Glorious","translit":"l-majīdi","root":"مجد","audio":"wbw/050_001_004.mp3"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"But they wonder that there has come to them a warner from among themselves, and the disbelievers say, \"This is an amazing thing.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"Nay","translit":"bal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَجِبُوٓا۟","english":"they wonder","translit":"ʿajibū","root":"عجب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَآءَهُم","english":"has come to them","translit":"jāahum","root":"جيأ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّنذِرٌۭ","english":"a warner","translit":"mundhirun","root":"نذر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِّنْهُمْ","english":"from them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَقَالَ","english":"So say","translit":"faqāla","root":"قول"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ","english":"the disbelievers","translit":"l-kāfirūna","root":"كفر"},{"position":9,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"This","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"شَىْءٌ","english":"(is) a thing","translit":"shayon","root":"شيأ"},{"position":11,"arabic":"عَجِيبٌ","english":"amazing","translit":"ʿajībun","root":"عجب"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"When we have died and have become dust, [we will return to life]? That is a distant return.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَءِذَا","english":"What! When","translit":"a-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِتْنَا","english":"we die","translit":"mit'nā","root":"موت"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَكُنَّا","english":"and have become","translit":"wakunnā","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُرَابًۭا ۖ","english":"dust","translit":"turāban","root":"ترب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_003_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"رَجْعٌۢ","english":"(is) a return","translit":"rajʿun","root":"رجع","audio":"wbw/050_003_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بَعِيدٌۭ","english":"far","translit":"baʿīdun","root":"بعد","audio":"wbw/050_003_008.mp3"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"We know what the earth diminishes of them, and with Us is a retaining record.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"Certainly","translit":"qad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلِمْنَا","english":"We know","translit":"ʿalim'nā","root":"علم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"تَنقُصُ","english":"diminishes","translit":"tanquṣu","root":"نقص"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضُ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍu","root":"أرض"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ ۖ","english":"of them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَعِندَنَا","english":"and with Us","translit":"waʿindanā","root":"عند","audio":"wbw/050_004_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبٌ","english":"(is) a Book","translit":"kitābun","root":"كتب","audio":"wbw/050_004_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"حَفِيظٌۢ","english":"guarded","translit":"ḥafīẓun","root":"حفظ","audio":"wbw/050_004_010.mp3"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"But they denied the truth when it came to them, so they are in a confused condition.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"Nay","translit":"bal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَذَّبُوا۟","english":"they denied","translit":"kadhabū","root":"كذب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ","english":"the truth","translit":"bil-ḥaqi","root":"حقق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَمَّا","english":"when","translit":"lammā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"جَآءَهُمْ","english":"it came (to) them","translit":"jāahum","root":"جيأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَهُمْ","english":"so they","translit":"fahum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِىٓ","english":"(are) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَمْرٍۢ","english":"a state","translit":"amrin","root":"أمر"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مَّرِيجٍ","english":"confused","translit":"marījin","root":"مرج"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"Have they not looked at the heaven above them - how We structured it and adorned it and [how] it has no rifts?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَفَلَمْ","english":"Then do not","translit":"afalam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَنظُرُوٓا۟","english":"they look","translit":"yanẓurū","root":"نظر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"at","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"the sky","translit":"l-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَوْقَهُمْ","english":"above them","translit":"fawqahum","root":"فوق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَيْفَ","english":"how","translit":"kayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بَنَيْنَـٰهَا","english":"We structured it","translit":"banaynāhā","root":"بني"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَزَيَّنَّـٰهَا","english":"and adorned it","translit":"wazayyannāhā","root":"زين"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"لَهَا","english":"for it","translit":"lahā","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"فُرُوجٍۢ","english":"rifts","translit":"furūjin","root":"فرج"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"And the earth - We spread it out and cast therein firmly set mountains and made grow therein [something] of every beautiful kind,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"And the earth","translit":"wal-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَدَدْنَـٰهَا","english":"We have spread it out","translit":"madadnāhā","root":"مدد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَأَلْقَيْنَا","english":"and cast","translit":"wa-alqaynā","root":"لقي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَوَٰسِىَ","english":"firmly set mountains","translit":"rawāsiya","root":"رسو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَنۢبَتْنَا","english":"and We made to grow","translit":"wa-anbatnā","root":"نبت"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"كُلِّ","english":"every","translit":"kulli","root":"كلل"},{"position":10,"arabic":"زَوْجٍۭ","english":"kind","translit":"zawjin","root":"زوج"},{"position":11,"arabic":"بَهِيجٍۢ","english":"beautiful","translit":"bahījin","root":"بهج"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"Giving insight and a reminder for every servant who turns [to Allah].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"تَبْصِرَةًۭ","english":"Giving insight","translit":"tabṣiratan","root":"بصر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَذِكْرَىٰ","english":"and a reminder","translit":"wadhik'rā","root":"ذكر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِكُلِّ","english":"for every","translit":"likulli","root":"كلل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَبْدٍۢ","english":"slave","translit":"ʿabdin","root":"عبد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّنِيبٍۢ","english":"who turns","translit":"munībin","root":"نوب"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And We have sent down blessed rain from the sky and made grow thereby gardens and grain from the harvest","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَنَزَّلْنَا","english":"And We have sent down","translit":"wanazzalnā","root":"نزل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"the sky","translit":"l-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَآءًۭ","english":"water","translit":"māan","root":"موه"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّبَـٰرَكًۭا","english":"blessed","translit":"mubārakan","root":"برك"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتْنَا","english":"then We made to grow","translit":"fa-anbatnā","root":"نبت"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"thereby","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","english":"gardens","translit":"jannātin","root":"جنن"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَحَبَّ","english":"and grain","translit":"waḥabba","root":"حبب"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْحَصِيدِ","english":"(for) the harvest","translit":"l-ḥaṣīdi","root":"حصد"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And lofty palm trees having fruit arranged in layers -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّخْلَ","english":"And the palms trees","translit":"wal-nakhla","root":"نخل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَاسِقَـٰتٍۢ","english":"tall","translit":"bāsiqātin","root":"بسق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَّهَا","english":"for it","translit":"lahā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"طَلْعٌۭ","english":"(are) layers","translit":"ṭalʿun","root":"طلع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَّضِيدٌۭ","english":"arranged","translit":"naḍīdun","root":"نضد"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"As provision for the servants, and We have given life thereby to a dead land. Thus is the resurrection.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"رِّزْقًۭا","english":"A provision","translit":"riz'qan","root":"رزق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلْعِبَادِ ۖ","english":"for the slaves","translit":"lil'ʿibādi","root":"عبد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَأَحْيَيْنَا","english":"and We give life","translit":"wa-aḥyaynā","root":"حيي","audio":"wbw/050_011_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"therewith","translit":"bihi","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_011_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَلْدَةًۭ","english":"(to) a land","translit":"baldatan","root":"بلد","audio":"wbw/050_011_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَّيْتًۭا ۚ","english":"dead","translit":"maytan","root":"موت","audio":"wbw/050_011_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","english":"Thus","translit":"kadhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_011_009.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْخُرُوجُ","english":"(will be) the coming forth","translit":"l-khurūju","root":"خرج","audio":"wbw/050_011_010.mp3"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"The people of Noah denied before them, and the companions of the well and Thamud","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَّبَتْ","english":"Denied","translit":"kadhabat","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَبْلَهُمْ","english":"before them","translit":"qablahum","root":"قبل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَوْمُ","english":"(the) people","translit":"qawmu","root":"قوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"نُوحٍۢ","english":"(of) Nuh","translit":"nūḥin","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَصْحَـٰبُ","english":"and (the) companions","translit":"wa-aṣḥābu","root":"صحب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسِّ","english":"(of) Ar-Raas","translit":"l-rasi","root":"رسس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَثَمُودُ","english":"and Thamud","translit":"wathamūdu","root":""}]},{"number":13,"translation":"And 'Aad and Pharaoh and the brothers of Lot","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَعَادٌۭ","english":"And Aad","translit":"waʿādun","root":"عود"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَفِرْعَوْنُ","english":"and Firaun","translit":"wafir'ʿawnu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَإِخْوَٰنُ","english":"and (the) brothers","translit":"wa-ikh'wānu","root":"أخو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لُوطٍۢ","english":"(of) Lut","translit":"lūṭin","root":""}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And the companions of the thicket and the people of Tubba'. All denied the messengers, so My threat was justly fulfilled.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَصْحَـٰبُ","english":"And (the) companions","translit":"wa-aṣḥābu","root":"صحب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْأَيْكَةِ","english":"(of) the wood","translit":"l-aykati","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَقَوْمُ","english":"and (the) people","translit":"waqawmu","root":"قوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُبَّعٍۢ ۚ","english":"(of) Tubba","translit":"tubbaʿin","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كُلٌّۭ","english":"All","translit":"kullun","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/050_014_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَذَّبَ","english":"denied","translit":"kadhaba","root":"كذب","audio":"wbw/050_014_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلرُّسُلَ","english":"the Messengers","translit":"l-rusula","root":"رسل","audio":"wbw/050_014_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَحَقَّ","english":"so was fulfilled","translit":"faḥaqqa","root":"حقق","audio":"wbw/050_014_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَعِيدِ","english":"My Threat","translit":"waʿīdi","root":"وعد","audio":"wbw/050_014_010.mp3"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"Did We fail in the first creation? But they are in confusion over a new creation.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَفَعَيِينَا","english":"Were We then tired","translit":"afaʿayīnā","root":"عيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱلْخَلْقِ","english":"with the creation","translit":"bil-khalqi","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَوَّلِ ۚ","english":"the first","translit":"l-awali","root":"أول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"Nay","translit":"bal","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_015_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_015_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(are) in","translit":"fī","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_015_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَبْسٍۢ","english":"doubt","translit":"labsin","root":"لبس","audio":"wbw/050_015_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِّنْ","english":"about","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_015_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"خَلْقٍۢ","english":"a creation","translit":"khalqin","root":"خلق","audio":"wbw/050_015_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"جَدِيدٍۢ","english":"new","translit":"jadīdin","root":"جدد","audio":"wbw/050_015_011.mp3"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"And We have already created man and know what his soul whispers to him, and We are closer to him than [his] jugular vein","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَا","english":"We created","translit":"khalaqnā","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ","english":"man","translit":"l-insāna","root":"أنس"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَنَعْلَمُ","english":"and We know","translit":"wanaʿlamu","root":"علم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"تُوَسْوِسُ","english":"whispers","translit":"tuwaswisu","root":"وسوس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"to him","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"نَفْسُهُۥ ۖ","english":"his soul","translit":"nafsuhu","root":"نفس"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَنَحْنُ","english":"and We","translit":"wanaḥnu","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_016_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَقْرَبُ","english":"(are) nearer","translit":"aqrabu","root":"قرب","audio":"wbw/050_016_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","english":"to him","translit":"ilayhi","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_016_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"than","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_016_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"حَبْلِ","english":"(his) jugular vein","translit":"ḥabli","root":"حبل","audio":"wbw/050_016_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلْوَرِيدِ","english":"(his) jugular vein","translit":"l-warīdi","root":"ورد","audio":"wbw/050_016_015.mp3"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"When the two receivers receive, seated on the right and on the left.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"When","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَتَلَقَّى","english":"receive","translit":"yatalaqqā","root":"لقي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَلَقِّيَانِ","english":"the two receivers","translit":"l-mutalaqiyāni","root":"لقي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَنِ","english":"on","translit":"ʿani","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْيَمِينِ","english":"the right","translit":"l-yamīni","root":"يمن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَعَنِ","english":"and on","translit":"waʿani","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلشِّمَالِ","english":"the left","translit":"l-shimāli","root":"شمل"},{"position":8,"arabic":"قَعِيدٌۭ","english":"seated","translit":"qaʿīdun","root":"قعد"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"Man does not utter any word except that with him is an observer prepared [to record].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"Not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَلْفِظُ","english":"he utters","translit":"yalfiẓu","root":"لفظ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَوْلٍ","english":"word","translit":"qawlin","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"but","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَدَيْهِ","english":"with him","translit":"ladayhi","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"رَقِيبٌ","english":"(is) an observer","translit":"raqībun","root":"رقب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَتِيدٌۭ","english":"ready","translit":"ʿatīdun","root":"عتد"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"And the intoxication of death will bring the truth; that is what you were trying to avoid.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَآءَتْ","english":"And will come","translit":"wajāat","root":"جيأ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سَكْرَةُ","english":"(the) stupor","translit":"sakratu","root":"سكر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتِ","english":"(of) death","translit":"l-mawti","root":"موت"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ ۖ","english":"in truth","translit":"bil-ḥaqi","root":"حقق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_019_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَا","english":"(is) what","translit":"mā","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_019_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كُنتَ","english":"you were","translit":"kunta","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/050_019_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِنْهُ","english":"[from it]","translit":"min'hu","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_019_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"تَحِيدُ","english":"avoiding","translit":"taḥīdu","root":"حيد","audio":"wbw/050_019_010.mp3"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"And the Horn will be blown. That is the Day of [carrying out] the threat.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَنُفِخَ","english":"And will be blown","translit":"wanufikha","root":"نفخ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"[in]","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلصُّورِ ۚ","english":"the trumpet","translit":"l-ṣūri","root":"صور"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_020_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/050_020_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْوَعِيدِ","english":"(of) the Warning","translit":"l-waʿīdi","root":"وعد","audio":"wbw/050_020_007.mp3"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"And every soul will come, with it a driver and a witness.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَآءَتْ","english":"And will come","translit":"wajāat","root":"جيأ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كُلُّ","english":"every","translit":"kullu","root":"كلل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَفْسٍۢ","english":"soul","translit":"nafsin","root":"نفس"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَّعَهَا","english":"with it","translit":"maʿahā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"سَآئِقٌۭ","english":"a driver","translit":"sāiqun","root":"سوق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَشَهِيدٌۭ","english":"and a witness","translit":"washahīdun","root":"شهد"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"[It will be said], \"You were certainly in unmindfulness of this, and We have removed from you your cover, so your sight, this Day, is sharp.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَّقَدْ","english":"Certainly","translit":"laqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كُنتَ","english":"you were","translit":"kunta","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"غَفْلَةٍۢ","english":"heedlessness","translit":"ghaflatin","root":"غفل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّنْ","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"this","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَكَشَفْنَا","english":"So We have removed","translit":"fakashafnā","root":"كشف"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَنكَ","english":"from you","translit":"ʿanka","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"غِطَآءَكَ","english":"your cover","translit":"ghiṭāaka","root":"غطو"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَبَصَرُكَ","english":"so your sight","translit":"fabaṣaruka","root":"بصر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمَ","english":"today","translit":"l-yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":12,"arabic":"حَدِيدٌۭ","english":"(is) sharp","translit":"ḥadīdun","root":"حدد"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"And his companion, [the angel], will say, \"This [record] is what is with me, prepared.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","english":"And (will) say","translit":"waqāla","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَرِينُهُۥ","english":"his companion","translit":"qarīnuhu","root":"قرن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"This","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَا","english":"(is) what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَدَىَّ","english":"(is) with me","translit":"ladayya","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَتِيدٌ","english":"ready","translit":"ʿatīdun","root":"عتد"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"[Allah will say], \"Throw into Hell every obstinate disbeliever,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَلْقِيَا","english":"Throw","translit":"alqiyā","root":"لقي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in (to)","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","english":"Hell","translit":"jahannama","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"كُلَّ","english":"every","translit":"kulla","root":"كلل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَفَّارٍ","english":"disbeliever","translit":"kaffārin","root":"كفر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَنِيدٍۢ","english":"stubborn","translit":"ʿanīdin","root":"عند"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"Preventer of good, aggressor, and doubter,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَّنَّاعٍۢ","english":"Forbidder","translit":"mannāʿin","root":"منع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلْخَيْرِ","english":"of good","translit":"lil'khayri","root":"خير"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مُعْتَدٍۢ","english":"transgressor","translit":"muʿ'tadin","root":"عدو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُّرِيبٍ","english":"doubter","translit":"murībin","root":"ريب"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"Who made [as equal] with Allah another deity; then throw him into the severe punishment.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"Who","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَعَلَ","english":"made","translit":"jaʿala","root":"جعل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَعَ","english":"with","translit":"maʿa","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهًا","english":"a god","translit":"ilāhan","root":"أله"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ءَاخَرَ","english":"another","translit":"ākhara","root":"أخر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَأَلْقِيَاهُ","english":"so throw him","translit":"fa-alqiyāhu","root":"لقي"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in(to)","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابِ","english":"the punishment","translit":"l-ʿadhābi","root":"عذب"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلشَّدِيدِ","english":"the severe","translit":"l-shadīdi","root":"شدد"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"His [devil] companion will say, \"Our Lord, I did not make him transgress, but he [himself] was in extreme error.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"۞ قَالَ","english":"Will say","translit":"qāla","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/050_027_002.mp3"},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَرِينُهُۥ","english":"his companion","translit":"qarīnuhu","root":"قرن","audio":"wbw/050_027_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبَّنَا","english":"Our Lord","translit":"rabbanā","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/050_027_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"not","translit":"mā","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_027_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَطْغَيْتُهُۥ","english":"I made him transgress","translit":"aṭghaytuhu","root":"طغي","audio":"wbw/050_027_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِن","english":"but","translit":"walākin","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_027_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"he was","translit":"kāna","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/050_027_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_027_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ضَلَـٰلٍۭ","english":"error","translit":"ḍalālin","root":"ضلل","audio":"wbw/050_027_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"بَعِيدٍۢ","english":"far","translit":"baʿīdin","root":"بعد","audio":"wbw/050_027_011.mp3"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"[Allah] will say, \"Do not dispute before Me, while I had already presented to you the warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","english":"He will say","translit":"qāla","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(Do) not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَخْتَصِمُوا۟","english":"dispute","translit":"takhtaṣimū","root":"خصم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَدَىَّ","english":"(in) My presence","translit":"ladayya","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","english":"and indeed","translit":"waqad","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"قَدَّمْتُ","english":"I sent forth","translit":"qaddamtu","root":"قدم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَيْكُم","english":"to you","translit":"ilaykum","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِٱلْوَعِيدِ","english":"the Warning","translit":"bil-waʿīdi","root":"وعد"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"The word will not be changed with Me, and never will I be unjust to the servants.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَا","english":"Not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُبَدَّلُ","english":"will be changed","translit":"yubaddalu","root":"بدل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْلُ","english":"the word","translit":"l-qawlu","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَدَىَّ","english":"with Me","translit":"ladayya","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"and not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَنَا۠","english":"I Am","translit":"anā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"بِظَلَّـٰمٍۢ","english":"unjust","translit":"biẓallāmin","root":"ظلم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لِّلْعَبِيدِ","english":"to My slaves","translit":"lil'ʿabīdi","root":"عبد"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"On the Day We will say to Hell, \"Have you been filled?\" and it will say, \"Are there some more,\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَقُولُ","english":"We will say","translit":"naqūlu","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِجَهَنَّمَ","english":"to Hell","translit":"lijahannama","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"هَلِ","english":"Are","translit":"hali","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱمْتَلَأْتِ","english":"you filled","translit":"im'talati","root":"ملأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَتَقُولُ","english":"And it will say","translit":"wataqūlu","root":"قول"},{"position":7,"arabic":"هَلْ","english":"Are","translit":"hal","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِن","english":"(there) any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"مَّزِيدٍۢ","english":"more","translit":"mazīdin","root":"زيد"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"And Paradise will be brought near to the righteous, not far,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأُزْلِفَتِ","english":"And will be brought near","translit":"wa-uz'lifati","root":"زلف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةُ","english":"the Paradise","translit":"l-janatu","root":"جنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"to the righteous","translit":"lil'muttaqīna","root":"وقي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"غَيْرَ","english":"not","translit":"ghayra","root":"غير"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَعِيدٍ","english":"far","translit":"baʿīdin","root":"بعد"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"[It will be said], \"This is what you were promised - for every returner [to Allah] and keeper [of His covenant]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"This","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَا","english":"(is) what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تُوعَدُونَ","english":"you were promised","translit":"tūʿadūna","root":"وعد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِكُلِّ","english":"for everyone","translit":"likulli","root":"كلل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَوَّابٍ","english":"who turns","translit":"awwābin","root":"أوب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"حَفِيظٍۢ","english":"(and) who keeps","translit":"ḥafīẓin","root":"حفظ"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"Who feared the Most Merciful unseen and came with a heart returning [in repentance].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَّنْ","english":"Who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَشِىَ","english":"feared","translit":"khashiya","root":"خشي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنَ","english":"the Most Gracious","translit":"l-raḥmāna","root":"رحم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْغَيْبِ","english":"in the unseen","translit":"bil-ghaybi","root":"غيب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَجَآءَ","english":"and came","translit":"wajāa","root":"جيأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِقَلْبٍۢ","english":"with a heart","translit":"biqalbin","root":"قلب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّنِيبٍ","english":"returning","translit":"munībin","root":"نوب"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"Enter it in peace. This is the Day of Eternity.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱدْخُلُوهَا","english":"Enter it","translit":"ud'khulūhā","root":"دخل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِسَلَـٰمٍۢ ۖ","english":"in peace","translit":"bisalāmin","root":"سلم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_034_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is) a Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/050_034_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْخُلُودِ","english":"(of) Eternity","translit":"l-khulūdi","root":"خلد","audio":"wbw/050_034_006.mp3"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"They will have whatever they wish therein, and with Us is more.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَهُم","english":"For them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"whatever","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَشَآءُونَ","english":"they wish","translit":"yashāūna","root":"شيأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَلَدَيْنَا","english":"and with Us","translit":"waladaynā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَزِيدٌۭ","english":"(is) more","translit":"mazīdun","root":"زيد"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"And how many a generation before them did We destroy who were greater than them in [striking] power and had explored throughout the lands. Is there any place of escape?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَمْ","english":"And how many","translit":"wakam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَهْلَكْنَا","english":"We destroyed","translit":"ahlaknā","root":"هلك"},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَبْلَهُم","english":"before them","translit":"qablahum","root":"قبل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"قَرْنٍ","english":"a generation","translit":"qarnin","root":"قرن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَشَدُّ","english":"(were) stronger","translit":"ashaddu","root":"شدد"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِنْهُم","english":"than them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"بَطْشًۭا","english":"(in) power","translit":"baṭshan","root":"بطش"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَنَقَّبُوا۟","english":"so they explored","translit":"fanaqqabū","root":"نقب"},{"position":11,"arabic":"فِى","english":"throughout","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْبِلَـٰدِ","english":"the lands","translit":"l-bilādi","root":"بلد"},{"position":13,"arabic":"هَلْ","english":"Is (there)","translit":"hal","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":15,"arabic":"مَّحِيصٍ","english":"place of escape","translit":"maḥīṣin","root":"حيص"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"Indeed in that is a reminder for whoever has a heart or who listens while he is present [in mind].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَذِكْرَىٰ","english":"surely, is a reminder","translit":"ladhik'rā","root":"ذكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لِمَن","english":"for (one) who","translit":"liman","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"قَلْبٌ","english":"a heart","translit":"qalbun","root":"قلب"},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَلْقَى","english":"(who) gives ear","translit":"alqā","root":"لقي"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمْعَ","english":"(who) gives ear","translit":"l-samʿa","root":"سمع"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"while he","translit":"wahuwa","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"شَهِيدٌۭ","english":"(is) a witness","translit":"shahīdun","root":"شهد"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"And We did certainly create the heavens and earth and what is between them in six days, and there touched Us no weariness.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَا","english":"We created","translit":"khalaqnā","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and whatever","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُمَا","english":"(is) between both of them","translit":"baynahumā","root":"بين"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"سِتَّةِ","english":"six","translit":"sittati","root":"ستت"},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَيَّامٍۢ","english":"periods","translit":"ayyāmin","root":"يوم"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and (did) not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"مَسَّنَا","english":"touch Us","translit":"massanā","root":"مسس"},{"position":12,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"لُّغُوبٍۢ","english":"fatigue","translit":"lughūbin","root":"لغب"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"So be patient, [O Muhammad], over what they say and exalt [Allah] with praise of your Lord before the rising of the sun and before its setting,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱصْبِرْ","english":"So be patient","translit":"fa-iṣ'bir","root":"صبر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"over","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَقُولُونَ","english":"they say","translit":"yaqūlūna","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَسَبِّحْ","english":"and glorify","translit":"wasabbiḥ","root":"سبح"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِحَمْدِ","english":"(the) praise","translit":"biḥamdi","root":"حمد"},{"position":7,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"قَبْلَ","english":"before","translit":"qabla","root":"قبل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"طُلُوعِ","english":"(the) rising","translit":"ṭulūʿi","root":"طلع"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلشَّمْسِ","english":"(of) the sun","translit":"l-shamsi","root":"شمس"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَقَبْلَ","english":"and before","translit":"waqabla","root":"قبل"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْغُرُوبِ","english":"the setting","translit":"l-ghurūbi","root":"غرب"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"And [in part] of the night exalt Him and after prostration.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","english":"And of","translit":"wamina","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّيْلِ","english":"the night","translit":"al-layli","root":"ليل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَسَبِّحْهُ","english":"glorify Him","translit":"fasabbiḥ'hu","root":"سبح"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَأَدْبَـٰرَ","english":"and after","translit":"wa-adbāra","root":"دبر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسُّجُودِ","english":"the prostration","translit":"l-sujūdi","root":"سجد"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"And listen on the Day when the Caller will call out from a place that is near -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱسْتَمِعْ","english":"And listen","translit":"wa-is'tamiʿ","root":"سمع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يُنَادِ","english":"will call","translit":"yunādi","root":"ندي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنَادِ","english":"the caller","translit":"l-munādi","root":"ندي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَّكَانٍۢ","english":"a place","translit":"makānin","root":"كون"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قَرِيبٍۢ","english":"near","translit":"qarībin","root":"قرب"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"The Day they will hear the blast [of the Horn] in truth. That is the Day of Emergence [from the graves].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسْمَعُونَ","english":"they will hear","translit":"yasmaʿūna","root":"سمع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلصَّيْحَةَ","english":"the Blast","translit":"l-ṣayḥata","root":"صيح"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ ۚ","english":"in truth","translit":"bil-ḥaqi","root":"حقق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_042_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/050_042_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْخُرُوجِ","english":"(of) coming forth","translit":"l-khurūji","root":"خرج","audio":"wbw/050_042_008.mp3"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"Indeed, it is We who give life and cause death, and to Us is the destination","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","english":"[We]","translit":"naḥnu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"نُحْىِۦ","english":"[We] give life","translit":"nuḥ'yī","root":"حيي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَنُمِيتُ","english":"and [We] cause death","translit":"wanumītu","root":"موت"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِلَيْنَا","english":"and to Us","translit":"wa-ilaynā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمَصِيرُ","english":"(is) the final return","translit":"l-maṣīru","root":"صير"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"On the Day the earth breaks away from them [and they emerge] rapidly; that is a gathering easy for Us.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَشَقَّقُ","english":"will split","translit":"tashaqqaqu","root":"شقق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضُ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍu","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَنْهُمْ","english":"from them","translit":"ʿanhum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"سِرَاعًۭا ۚ","english":"hurrying","translit":"sirāʿan","root":"سرع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_044_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"حَشْرٌ","english":"(is) a gathering","translit":"ḥashrun","root":"حشر","audio":"wbw/050_044_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَيْنَا","english":"for Us","translit":"ʿalaynā","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_044_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يَسِيرٌۭ","english":"easy","translit":"yasīrun","root":"يسر","audio":"wbw/050_044_010.mp3"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"We are most knowing of what they say, and you are not over them a tyrant. But remind by the Qur'an whoever fears My threat.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"نَّحْنُ","english":"We","translit":"naḥnu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","english":"know best","translit":"aʿlamu","root":"علم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"[of] what","translit":"bimā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَقُولُونَ ۖ","english":"they say","translit":"yaqūlūna","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"and not","translit":"wamā","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_045_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَنتَ","english":"(are) you","translit":"anta","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_045_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِم","english":"over them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_045_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِجَبَّارٍۢ ۖ","english":"the one to compel","translit":"bijabbārin","root":"جبر","audio":"wbw/050_045_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فَذَكِّرْ","english":"But remind","translit":"fadhakkir","root":"ذكر","audio":"wbw/050_045_011.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"بِٱلْقُرْءَانِ","english":"with the Quran","translit":"bil-qur'āni","root":"قرأ","audio":"wbw/050_045_012.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"مَن","english":"whoever","translit":"man","root":"","audio":"wbw/050_045_013.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"يَخَافُ","english":"fears","translit":"yakhāfu","root":"خوف","audio":"wbw/050_045_014.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَعِيدِ","english":"My threat","translit":"waʿīdi","root":"وعد","audio":"wbw/050_045_015.mp3"}]}]}
